==================================================
IMPORTANT REQUIREMENTS
==================================================

Do not design this as a generic corporate website.

The primary product is the AI chatbot information service.

Make the chatbot interface one of the most visually important parts of the system.

Make Knowledge Base Management, Conversation Monitoring, Unanswered Questions, User Feedback, and Analytics the core admin features.

Do not add KP/Magang registration, application submission, document verification, participant monitoring, or internship administration features.

The website only focuses on AI chatbot information services for Kerja Praktik and Magang.

The chatbot must clearly communicate that answers are generated from official knowledge base documents.

Prioritize transparency by displaying source citations.

Create consistent reusable components and Auto Layout.

Use proper Figma layer naming.

Use component variants.

Create desktop, tablet, and mobile responsive layouts.

The final result should be suitable for:
- Kerja Praktik project.
- Academic presentation.
- System demonstration.
- Usability testing.
- Implementation reference for Laravel and FastAPI development.